label: contactPointInfo
comment: Contact point information of a individual/business/service corresponding to this observation.

label: localeInfo
comment: Locale information corresponding to this observation.

label: personnelInfo
comment: Personal information of the individual/business/service corresponding to this observation.

label: foundingDate
comment: The date when the association/business/market was established.

label: marketID
comment: The unique ID referring to the agricultural market establishment corresponding to this observation

label: insurancePremium
comment: The amount that is paid by the individual or business for availing the insurance policy.

label: marketName
comment: Name of the market corresponding to this observation

label: marketFee
comment: The amount of money payable by a trader/farmer to use the Stall/Unit in a market corresponding to this observation.

label: marketValuation
comment: The total worth of the market which means the total arrival quantity with the price of the commodity .

label: amcGrade
comment: The grade assigned by the Agricultural Market Committee corresponding to this observation.

label: amcName
comment: The name of the Agricultural Market Committee corresponding to this observation.

label: amcCode
comment: The unique code assigned to the Agricultural Market Committee corresponding to this observation.

label: agencyName
comment: The agency which procures the commodity corresponding to this observation.

label: observationDateTime
comment: Last reported time of observation.

label: farmerCount
comment: The total number of farmers registered with the market corresponding to this observation.

label: traderCount
comment: The total number of traders registered with the market corresponding to this observation.

label: commissionAgentCount
comment: The total number of commission agents registered with the market corresponding to this observation.

label: govtAgencyCount
comment: The total number of government agencies corresponding to this observation.

label: commodityInfo
comment: The information about the agricultural produce/commodity associated with the AMC/market corresponding to this observation.

label: amcID
comment: The unique ID assigned to the Agricultural Market Committee corresponding to this observation.

label: orgBranches
comment: The branches or sub units of an organisation at different geographical locations.

label: areaServed
comment: The list of geographic areas (states, districts) served by the entity.

label: mediaURL
comment: Link(s) to any image(s) or media of the entity or incident corresponding to this observation

label: landExtent
comment: Area of the land corresponding to this observation.

label: weighBridgeCapacity
comment: The maximum capacity of the weighing bridge corresponding to this observation.

label: auctionShedNumber
comment: The unique identifier for the auction shed corresponding to this observation.

label: auctionShedSpace
comment: The total land area of the market/mandi allocated for auctioning of commodities.

label: officeSpace
comment: The total land area allocated for administrative purposes of a business or market corresponding to this observation.

label: warehouseSpace
comment: The total land area allocated for the storage of commodities in the market/mandi corresponding to this observation.

label: registrationNumber
comment: The registration number of the entity corresponding to this observation.

label: location
comment: The physical location of the entity corresponding to the observation.

label: language
comment: Represents the language(s) that can be used for communicating with an entity or those offered by a service corresponding to this observation.

label: capitalInfo
comment: The income and expenditure information corresponding to the entity.
